I made boundaries more smooth and gave an instruction panel. Also creating some levels of enemies that shoot towards the player. There is an issue though, somehow, once the player dies, the image or gifs do not display, I will need to fix that after this patch.

Cleansed Window class. Removed Chest Room and Shop.
